md](https://github.com/cssnano/cssnano/blob/master/CONTRIBUTORS.md).\n\n## License\n\nMIT © [Ben Briggs](http://beneb.info)\n\n[postcss]: https://github.com/postcss/postcss\n","readmeFilename":"README.md"}